<task id="R7-004" project="spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r7">
  <metadata>
    <title>Implement IOpenAiClient.GetStructuredCompletionRawAsync call + JsonElement binding</title>
    <status>not-started</status>
    <wave>1</wave>
    <estimated-effort>2-3 hours</estimated-effort>
    <tags>bff-api, code-impl, wave-1</tags>
    <rigor-level>FULL</rigor-level>
    <parallel-safe>true</parallel-safe>
    <dependencies>003</dependencies>
    <fr-coverage>FR-12 (LLM invocation + output binding)</fr-coverage>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
    Wire the IOpenAiClient.GetStructuredCompletionRawAsync call into AiCompletionNodeExecutor.ExecuteAsync()
    using the merged (SystemPrompt, OutputSchema, Temperature) tuple produced by task 003. Bind the response
    to JsonElement and write it to node.OutputVariable via NodeOutput.Ok. Wrap LLM errors as NodeOutput.Error
    with NodeErrorCodes.LlmCallFailed (or matching existing code) — the test in task 009 will assert this
    error path.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    Senior .NET backend developer completing the AiCompletionNodeExecutor happy-path. Mirror AiAnalysisNodeExecutor's
    call to IOpenAiClient — same retry envelope, same telemetry tags, same error mapping. Do NOT introduce a new
    retry policy or new error code class.
  </role>

  <goal>
    AiCompletionNodeExecutor.ExecuteAsync() complete happy-path:
    1. Invokes IOpenAiClient.GetStructuredCompletionRawAsync with merged SystemPrompt + OutputSchema + Temperature
    2. Receives raw structured-completion response (JsonElement or string-then-parsed)
    3. Binds the parsed JsonElement to node.OutputVariable via NodeOutput.Ok
    4. Emits standard ActivitySource telemetry tags (node.id, action_type=AiCompletion, llm.deployment, llm.tokens)
    5. Wraps LLM HTTP errors / malformed responses as NodeOutput.Error with appropriate NodeErrorCodes value
    6. Honors CancellationToken (propagates to IOpenAiClient call)
    7. Compiles clean; existing test suite green
  </goal>

  <inputs>
    <file purpose="executor-with-merge-applied">src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Nodes/AiCompletionNodeExecutor.cs</file>
    <file purpose="pattern-decision">projects/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r7/notes/spikes/aicompletion-pattern-decision.md</file>
