    <file purpose="bff-constraints">.claude/constraints/bff-extensions.md</file>
  </inputs>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-010">DI Minimalism — IOpenAiClient is already injected (task 002 ctor); no new dependencies.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">BFF AI Architecture — direct dependency on IOpenAiClient is allowed inside Services/Ai/ (this is the AI internals boundary). Do NOT introduce a facade type.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-029">BFF Publish Hygiene — task 010 runs full publish + CVE; this task contributes another small delta.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-038">Testing Strategy — task 009 mocks IOpenAiClient at the executor boundary. Do NOT use Mock&lt;HttpMessageHandler&gt;. The error-mapping code added in this task is what task 009 asserts.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec FR-12">Pattern: Call IOpenAiClient.GetStructuredCompletionRawAsync; parse response to JsonElement; bind to node.OutputVariable.</constraint>
    <constraint source="CLAUDE.md §10">BFF Hygiene — placement decision unchanged from task 002 (IN BFF, leaf executor).</constraint>
